00:29:04,390 --> 00:29:04,780
You're welcome.

597
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:08,870
Coming.

598
00:29:09,230 --> 00:29:09,460
Come.

599
00:29:12,910 --> 00:29:13,660
How about it?

600
00:29:13,910 --> 00:29:14,750
Have you figured it out?

601
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:16,340
Are you really going to take part in the dragon boat race?

602
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:19,140
It's different this time.

603
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:21,180
I really want to play with everyone.

604
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:26,980
Okay.

605
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:28,710
I won't be here

606
00:29:28,710 --> 00:29:30,300
