723
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:31,430
What?

724
00:33:32,780 --> 00:33:34,430
Did he train secretly?

725
00:33:36,910 --> 00:33:37,710
Looks like

726
00:33:37,870 --> 00:33:38,910
