727
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:43,260
♪In the best years...♪

728
00:33:43,910 --> 00:33:45,180
Look at him.

729
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:47,300
He secretly trained.

730
00:33:49,710 --> 00:33:50,460
Look at his details.

731
00:33:50,460 --> 00:33:51,590
You can learn from him.

732
00:33:53,870 --> 00:33:54,820
Right.

733
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:57,910
