♪The mist rising as we pass through♪

758
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:43,700
♪Rain-soaked alleys♪

759
00:35:43,740 --> 00:35:46,700
♪Watching the relentless downpour♪

760
00:35:46,740 --> 00:35:47,620
♪So unreasonable♪

761
00:35:47,660 --> 00:35:49,420
♪A brief pause♪

